{
  "description": "A nighttime panoramic view of a city skyline illuminated with bright lights, featuring a dramatic fireworks display. A long bridge stretches across a dark body of water in the foreground, its lights reflecting on the water's surface. The city skyline is densely packed with buildings, many of which are lit up, creating a vibrant urban glow.  Fireworks explode in the sky above, appearing as bursts of red, white, and blue.  A hilly landscape can be seen in the mid-ground, partially obscuring the base of the buildings. The overall scene evokes a celebratory and dynamic atmosphere.",
